          { "feature": "urine_chloride_gt_20_saline_resistant", "weight": 4 },
          { "feature": "hypokalemia_often_present", "weight": 3 }
        ],
        "management": "Saline-responsive (urine Cl <20): volume repletion with NS, K+ replacement. Saline-resistant (urine Cl >20): hold diuretics, treat hyperaldosteronism (spironolactone), consider acetazolamide if severe."
      },
      {
